==========================================

Private Credentials & Secrets (CRITICAL)

==========================================

Never commit your local keys to GitHub.

.env
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

==========================================

Local SQLite/JSON Database Backups

==========================================

Excludes local transaction logs and simulated user credential backups.

user_database.json
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

